text: Artemio Villaseñor Panganiban Jr. (born December 7, 1937) is a Filipino politician and lawyer. He was born in Manila. Panganiban was the 21st Supreme Court Chief Justice of the Philippines from December 2005 to December 2007. ==References== ==Other websites== *Supreme Court of the Philippines *Website – Spreading the Gospel of Liberty and Prosperity under the Rule of Law Category:1937 births Category:Living people Category:Chief justices of the Supreme Court of the Philippines Category:Politicians from Manila Category:Lawyers from Manila
